<section class="features-section" style="padding-top: 0;">
    <h2 class="section-heading">Who is Melodic for?</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Built for developers who value understanding their tools.</p>
    <div class="features" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);">
        <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>API Developers</h3>
            <p>Building JSON APIs with clear data access patterns. CQRS queries and commands, JWT authentication, and structured error responses out of the box.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>PHP Modernizers</h3>
            <p>Teams moving from legacy PHP to modern practices. PHP 8.2+ features, constructor injection, typed properties, and clean separation of concerns.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>Control-Oriented Developers</h3>
            <p>Developers who want to understand every line of their framework. No hidden behavior, no convention-over-configuration surprises, no magic string resolution.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

